precis:
Re-appointment of the following persons as part-time members of the
Canadian Human Rights Commission to hold office during good behaviour for
a term of two years, effective October 31, 1998.
(ROBINSON KOILPILLAI, of Edmonton, Alberta; and MARY Mac LENNAN, of
Halifax, Nova Scotia)
